{{勞工}}
'''六小時工作制'''是一種有關勞動時間的提案，主張[[勞動者|勞動者]]每天工作時間不超過六小時。這個工作時間比普遍採用的[[八小时工作制|八小时工作制]]要短。縮短工作時間的提案除了六小時工作制外，還有每週工作四天的[[四天工作制|四天工作制]]，一般認為六小時工作制比四天工作制要好<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-01-13/long-weekends-alluring-shorter-working-day-more-practical/11862662|title=Time's up for the 9-to-5 — a six-hour working day is the future|last=Veal|first=Anthony|date=2020-01-13|website=ABC News|language=en-AU|access-date=2020-01-16|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819202420/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2020-01-13/long-weekends-alluring-shorter-working-day-more-practical/11862662|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 各地情况 ==
===澳大利亚===
[[澳大利亚绿党|澳大利亚绿党]]支持[[四天工作制|四天工作制]]及六小时工作制<ref>{{cite news |title=Australian party pitches four-day working week |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-39263455 |access-date=2020-10-14 |work=BBC News |date=2017-03-14 |archive-date=2021-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107085640/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-australia-39263455 }}</ref>。

=== 芬兰 ===
2020年，[[芬兰|芬兰]]总理[[桑娜·马林|桑娜·马林]]宣布支持六小时工作制<ref>{{cite news |title=Finland Is Rallying Around a Six-Hour Workday — And So Should We |url=https://jacobinmag.com/2020/09/finland-six-hour-workday-working-hours-covid |access-date=2020-10-14 |work=[[雅各宾_(杂志)|Jacobin]] |archive-date=2022-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524010915/https://jacobinmag.com/2020/09/finland-six-hour-workday-working-hours-covid }}</ref>。

=== 挪威 ===
挪威[[红党_(挪威)|红党]]支持六小时工作制<ref>{{cite news |title=Six-hour workday |url=https://roedt.no/sekstimersdag |access-date=17 September 2021 |work=Rødt |date=2021-09-17 |archive-date=2021-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211010114704/https://roedt.no/sekstimersdag }}</ref>。

=== 瑞典 ===
[[瑞典|瑞典]]曾數次小規模的實施六小時工作制，包括私人公司以及公營機構<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/business-34677949|title=The truth about Sweden's short working hours|last=Savage|first=Maddy|date=2015-11-02|access-date=2020-01-16|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111202406/https://www.bbc.com/news/business-34677949|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[哥德堡|哥德堡]]曾進行一項實驗，有七十名護理師在十八個月內進行六小時工作制，結果病假人數減少，健康的自評情形比較好，生產力也提昇了，但整体开销仍上升了1200万[[瑞典克朗|瑞典克朗]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/business-38843341|title=What really happened when Swedes tried six-hour days?|last=Savage|first=Maddy|date=2017-02-08|access-date=2020-01-16|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213134432/https://www.bbc.com/news/business-38843341|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過反對者認為病假比例減少的程度不大，而耗費的成本很高，後來此計劃沒有繼續<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/topic/newsworld/109/201802010003.aspx|title=想減工時？瑞典人更關心彈性工時|author=黃齡儀|date=2018-02-01|access-date=2020-07-17|language=zh|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820114157/https://www.cna.com.tw/topic/newsworld/109/201802010003.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

